subSubSection.paragraph:
Abdomen:
In ventral view, ventrites IV-IX visible (
Fig. 16
), in dorsal view tergites I-VII about equal in length and decreasing in width (
Fig.17
),segmentsVII-IX clearly and gradually reduced;5 spiracles present,positioned on pleura I-V, bicameral (
Fig. 18
);pseudocerci inconspicuous at segment IX, unpigmented; in ventral view, ventrites IV-VIII with 1 pair of setae; in dorsal view,tergites I-IX without setae.
